%h1
  Information

%p
  For preregistration on races
  = link_to 'registration', new_racer_path
  is required.
%p
  To make a preregistration on the race you need to be logged on the page and
  select the application on the
  = link_to 'race menu', races_path
  "Prijavi se / Sign in". If you log out of the site, please use the e-mail
  address and mobile phone number in the format you entered when registering to
  re-apply.

%p
  For any problems, please contact us on email.
  %a{ href: 'mailto:stoperica.timing@gmail.com' }
    stoperica.timing(a)gmail.com

%p
  On mobile devices, the page is best viewed on
  %a{ href: 'https://www.google.com/chrome/browser/mobile/' }
    Google Chrome web browser.

